{"tid":499746,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"難民之父張超雄：你惡哂喇，睇你惡得幾耐","createTime":"2017-12-15T07:03:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T09:21:33.000Z","uid":41404,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3f2b282fbc4a270b70b0813650dca2af71bae0f9","tid":499746,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T07:03:42.000Z","msg":"<strong>工黨張超雄在發言時反駁民建聯陳克勤指摘民主派沒有開會，張指不出席會議是「抗爭」，反問「如果我哋偷懶點會返來（立法會）？」認為偷懶的是零票當選的建制派，不需要向選民交待，又指要改的不是《議事規則》，而是功能組別。<br />\n<br />\n他批評，向建制派「講道理都係嘥氣」，建制派的使命只是「保住政府、護航」，令他們和政府可以繼續「圍威喂」，令社會不能平衡、公義和關愛。他又指，出任議員10年，對議會非常失望，建制派在議會「惡慣左」，「被權力腐化」，只會話民主派的聲音刺耳；同時要求民主派「守規矩」，但規矩會轉移，怒斥「你惡哂喇，睇你惡得幾耐」。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171215/57584936\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171215%2F57584936&d=O1HfhjmKIZ%2BMAfpPFEUQrE4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=120b9520\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171215%2F57584936&h=4a981e6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171215/57584936</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a1097bc3aca53c2d88d97c233f8f66258de3d52","tid":499746,"uid":47359,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T07:27:36.000Z","msg":"好心做唔到咁多嘢就咪撚咁大口氣啦<br />\n的確保蝗黨而家係玩哂<br />\n尤其對手係含撚泛民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45792d9984efa5c9adaba08903e25451de563b21","tid":499746,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T08:36:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9be911f5ae40866396a04990f08ef6a1396d103a","tid":499746,"uid":50101,"like":0,"dislike"